{"tid":2077768,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"貿發局：書商參展須自律  業界自我審查「有英女皇皇冠驚犯法」","createTime":"2020-06-24T13:56:11.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-24T14:15:52.000Z","uid":25558,"like":1,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"71104383cca56a2d2a4b583022613e2c2d504fde","tid":2077768,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-24T13:56:11.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20200624/Q6BPTQ2DQDPKOTGHOU5M3R6QPU/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200624%2FQ6BPTQ2DQDPKOTGHOU5M3R6QPU%2F&d=Dkz3eIcuz1ZryPyeMF8ZPuF5TOcUp1XGW39uuIwQJ%2Fg%3D&h=dcf4bfcd\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200624%2FQ6BPTQ2DQDPKOTGHOU5M3R6QPU%2F&h=84d740a9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20200624/Q6BPTQ2DQDPKOTGHOU5M3R6QPU/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n貿發局：書商參展須自律 <br />\n業界自我審查「有英女皇皇冠驚犯法」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/MUXEXRVSAQS4STYS4FB7SBRXYI.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FMUXEXRVSAQS4STYS4FB7SBRXYI.gif&h=29ddcaf3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n不少作者以香港抗爭運動等時事題材出版書籍，隨港版國安法將落實，業界紛紛擔心會踩中紅線。<br />\n<br />\n【惡法臨城】<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】港版國安法即將落實，今年書展或成法例實施後第一個文化展覽。主辦書展的貿發局副總裁周啟良回應會否審查書刊時稱，書展「從來都冇censorship（審查制度），要靠業界自律」。有參展商認為，出版業自我審查問題越趨嚴重，「業界會驚做唔做？印唔印？」有書店創辦人則指貿發局言論多此一舉，製造寒蟬效應。<br />\n<br />\n過去有不少參展商在書展擺賣政治書，對於港版國安法壓境，貿發局會否主動審查書商？周啟良昨回應時強調，書展從來。。。。掃（港）獨」，他強調書展是一家大小、鼓勵健康閱讀的地方，籲公眾表達政治訴求時不要影響他人，否則會要求離場。<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：刑事案法官絕非特首指派<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/PAGHBR47PCLBW5QH6LUZPZPALM.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FPAGHBR47PCLBW5QH6LUZPZPALM.gif&h=b050121b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n周啟良<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n書室創辦人斥製寒蟬效應<br />\n<br />\n書展參展商CUP媒體執行總編輯陶培康表示，港版國安法條文未公佈，業界對於法例存在很多疑問，「之前做落、印落（啲書）又得唔得呢？」即使未有港版國安法前，「大家都越來越驚，會擔心，唔敢做」。他又指，書展擺賣的書籍暫時沒有改變，「但有晒心理準備（可能會變），最終都係睇條文」。<br />\n<br />\n陶培康續說，對港版國安法感到擔心和憂慮，「實際上未出，好難講點影響。我哋有本書叫《THIS IS HONG KONG 從前，。。。。<br />\n<br />\n序言書室創辦人李達寧雖未曾參與書展，但認為貿發局的回應「好怪」，反。。。。，暫時持觀望態度，「如果講明禁書名單，因為犯法都會下架」。"},{"pid":"c206b73e79316cbb275d9eab703e7a496525872b","tid":2077768,"uid":100581,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-24T13:57:17.000Z","msg":"你驚咪中招囉"},{"pid":"da3bfc990475532b829a341d70dd6e8530de5ba1","tid":2077768,"uid":263648,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"71104383cca56a2d2a4b583022613e2c2d504fde","tid":2077768,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-24T13:56:11.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20200624/Q6BPTQ2DQDPKOTGHOU5M3R6QPU/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200624%2FQ6BPTQ2DQDPKOTGHOU5M3R6QPU%2F&d=Dkz3eIcuz1ZryPyeMF8ZPuF5TOcUp1XGW39uuIwQJ%2Fg%3D&h=dcf4bfcd\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200624%2FQ6BPTQ2DQDPKOTGHOU5M3R6QPU%2F&h=84d740a9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20200624/Q6BPTQ2DQDPKOTGHOU5M3R6QPU/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n貿發局：書商參展須自律 <br />\n業界自我審查「有英女皇皇冠驚犯法」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/MUXEXRVSAQS4STYS4FB7SBRXYI.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FMUXEXRVSAQS4STYS4FB7SBRXYI.gif&h=29ddcaf3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n不少作者以香港抗爭運動等時事題材出版書籍，隨港版國安法將落實，業界紛紛擔心會踩中紅線。<br />\n<br />\n【惡法臨城】<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】港版國安法即將落實，今年書展或成法例實施後第一個文化展覽。主辦書展的貿發局副總裁周啟良回應會否審查書刊時稱，書展「從來都冇censorship（審查制度），要靠業界自律」。有參展商認為，出版業自我審查問題越趨嚴重，「業界會驚做唔做？印唔印？」有書店創辦人則指貿發局言論多此一舉，製造寒蟬效應。<br /